show.description: A fearless and clever maid enters the Forbidden City, determined to uncover her sister’s murder. Surrounded by palace intrigue, betrayals, and unexpected love, her quest for justice transforms her destiny. From servant to powerful consort, this is a tale of ambition, survival, and unbreakable will.
